Hello again and for the last time.

00:00:02.895 --> 00:00:05.880
Congratulations on making it this far.

00:00:05.880 --> 00:00:09.120
Here's what we learned over the last few lessons.

00:00:09.120 --> 00:00:12.375
We started out looking at costs in the cloud,

00:00:12.375 --> 00:00:15.465
and how to monitor and optimize them.

00:00:15.465 --> 00:00:18.675
Next, we looked at performance,

00:00:18.675 --> 00:00:22.695
starting with scaling and then taking a deep dive into storage,

00:00:22.695 --> 00:00:25.290
archive, and database options.

